      \u003C/graphic>\n         \u003C/surface> -->\n    \u003C/facsimile>\n    \u003Ctext>\n        \u003Cbody>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"edition\" subtype=\"primary\" xml:space=\"preserve\" xml:lang=\"la\" resp=\"#AA\" source=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/GQN8UZSI\">\n                \u003Cab>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"1\"/>\u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>Imp\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>eratori\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> Caesari \u003Cname>\u003Cdel rend=\"erasure\">Domitiano\u003C/del>\u003C/name>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"2\"/>\u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>Aug\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>usto\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> Germanico\n                    \u003Clb n=\"3\"/>\u003CroleName type=\"supracivic.religious\" subtype=\"pontifex.maximus\">\u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>pont\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>ifici\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> \u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>max\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>imo\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan>\u003C/roleName> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> \u003CroleName type=\"supracivic\" subtype=\"tribunicia.potestas\">\u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>trib\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>unicia\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> \u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>pot\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>estate\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan>\u003C/roleName> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> \u003Cnum value=\"3\">III\u003C/num>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"4\"/>\u003CroleName type=\"supracivic\" subtype=\"imperator\">\u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>Imp\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>eratori\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan>\u003C/roleName> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> \u003Cnum value=\"7\">VII\u003C/num> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> \u003CroleName type=\"supracivic\" subtype=\"consul\">\u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>co\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>n\u003C/ex>\u003Cabbr>s\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>uli\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan>\u003C/roleName> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> \u003Cnum value=\"10\">X\u003C/num> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> \u003CroleName type=\"supracivic\" subtype=\"pater.patriae\">\u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>p\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>atri\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> \u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>p\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>atriae\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan>\u003C/roleName>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"5\"/>opus \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> aquae \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> ductus \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> exstructum \n                    \u003Clb n=\"6\"/>supra \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> terram \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> et \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> lapidibus\n                    \u003Clb n=\"7\"/>quadratis \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> a \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> novo \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> tectum\n                \u003C/ab>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"apparatus\">\n                \u003ClistApp>\u003Capp>\u003Cnote>Text of CIL\u003C/note>\u003C/app>\u003C/listApp>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"en\" resp=\"#AA\">\n                \u003Cp>To Imperator Caesar Domitianus Augustus Germanicus, pontifex maximus, with tribunician power for the third time, imperator for the 7th time, consul for the 10th time, father of the fatherland. The work of an aqueduct was constructed above ground and newly covered with squared stones ... \u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"commentary\">\n                \u003Cp>It appears that the name of Domitian was subject to damnatio memoriae\u003C!--commented out pending revision-->\n                    \u003C!--?with damn mem. of Domitian's name? Imp. Caesari domitiano Aug Germanico pont max trib pot III imp VII cos X P P opus aquae ductus exstructum supra terram et lapidibus quadratis a novo tectum [ stone  breaks off. See also  M. Horster, BauinschriftenrömischerKaiser (Stuttgart 2001) 342-343,  Nr. XII 2-->\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"CIL\">\n                        \u003Cauthor>Mommsen\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1883\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>\n                            \u003Cref target=\"http://arachne.uni-koeln.de/books/CILv10pII1883\">7227\u003C/ref>\n                        \u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/GQN8UZSI\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Manganaro\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1988\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>72\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/RZSFKACR\"/>\n                        \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001427\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001427\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                \u003C/listBibl>\n\t   \u003ClistBibl type=\"discussion\">\u003Cbibl/>\u003C/listBibl>\n            \u003C/div>\n        \u003C/body>\n    \u003C/text>\n\u003C/TEI>\n"],"uses":{"params":["slug"]}}]}
